    Let error_list be proc memory_get_int64 from Layout with analyzer, 48
    Let error_msg be proc create_string from StringCore with message

    proc list_push from List with error_list, error_msg

    Return 1
End Process

Process called "add_type_warning" takes analyzer as Integer, message as Integer returns Integer:
